        <h2> CONSUMER ADVOCACY</h2>
        <p>Assured Performance is building a national Original Equipment Manufacturer (OEM) driven, consumer focused Preferred Provider Network. In doing so, we are empowering our member shops to be Preferred Provider Organizations (PPOs). This gives consumers the ability to make the right choice when selecting a collision repair facility - a Certified Collision Care Provider. This helps to ensure that consumers can find a safe choice wherever and whenever they need a repair.</p>
