<div id="wrap">
    <p id="pcont">As a "Certified Collision Care Provider,"you receive shop-branded VIP Collision Care loyalty cards and other tools to promote you shop's exclusive status and enhance your relationship with customers. These marketing and promotional tools, gives you a unique competitive advantage in your local market.</p>
    <div id="div0">
        <img id="lpimg" src="<?= base_url() ?>resources/common/images/Certifiedsign.png" alt="certifiedSign"/>
        <p id="rpcontents"><span id="hc">SIGNAGE</span>Receive one 18x23 Certified Collision Care Provider sign which Assured Performance branded. Optional exterior and interior signs are also available for "Certified Collision Care Providers. "Upon official Certification you can also receive optional signage from various OEMs and strategic partners</p>
    </div>
    <div id="div1">
        <img id="rpimg" src="<?= base_url() ?>resources/common/images/VIPcard.png" alt="vipcard"/>
        <p id="lpcontents"><span id="hc">IN-NETWORK VIP CARDS</span>To ensure customer satisfaction and improve your customer retention, give your customers In-Network VIP Cards to refer to your shop when they are in need of your services. With these cards, your collision repair business has an effective loyalty program backed by Assured Performance Collision Care. In addition, the In-Network VIP Cards will be customized with your logo and business information to ensure it markets only your brand.</p>
    </div>
    <div id="div2">
        <img id="lpimg" src="<?= base_url() ?>resources/common/images/lobbyroom.png" alt="lobbyroom"/>
        <p id="rpcontents"><span id="hc">CONSUMER EDUCATION LOBBY VIDEO</span>Help educate the consumer on repair processes and your facility. The video is customized for your shop and ranges from 3.5 minutes to 25 minutes, with multiple segments. You can even have a business profile video made which incorporates your own images into the video for a fee.</p>
    </div>
    <div id="div3">
        <img id="rpimg" src="<?= base_url() ?>resources/common/images/pressrelease.png" alt="lobbyroom"/>
        <p id="lpcontents"><span id="hc">PRESS RELEASE</span>Press release will be written and distributed for your shop upon successful completion of Certification. Cost includes sourcing of media outlets for your shop's market area, electronic distribution and customization of the press release template to include specifics to your shop. You can also have a press release sent to your local television, radio and media outlets announcing your prestigious accomplishment for an additional cost.</p>
    </div>
    <div id="div4"><img id="lpimg" src="<?= base_url() ?>resources/common/images/website.png" alt="lobbyroom"/>
        <p id="rpcontents"><span id="hc">WEBSITE</span>Expand your business and draw in new customer with a professional website. There will be an integration of In-Network VIP Card registration and program details into your shop's existing website (includes micro-site for locator). For an additional cost, you can choose from one of our pre-designed website templates to create or revamp your current website.</p>
    </div>
